177
00:11:18,708 --> 00:11:23,503
Like I still hope, that
whoever he is, is a nice guy.

178
00:11:23,587 --> 00:11:26,465
That like, maybe that night
was just a bad misunderstanding,

179
00:11:26,549 --> 00:11:28,217
or a night gone wrong,

180
00:11:29,593 --> 00:11:32,388
or he had a bad day, or his
parents got in a car crash.

181
