higher I go, the longer I stay. Until…

193
00:12:36,457 --> 00:12:42,171
He's been, um, ahem,
very loving the last few days.

194
00:12:42,296 --> 00:12:46,133
-But at some point he gets the power back.
-Mm.

195
00:12:49,304 --> 00:12:52,224
Usually when my bruises fade…

196
00:12:54,309 --> 00:12:56,144
…and he doesn't feel as guilty.

197
00:12:56,228 --> 00:13:00,064
He feels insecure, and
then it all happens again.

198
00:13:00,148 --> 00:13:01,441
Where is he now?

199
00:13:01,525 --> 00:13:04,237
He is in Phoenix. He left this morning.

200
00:13:09,367 --> 00:13:11,828
When are you going to leave him, Celeste?

201
00:13:12,745 --> 00:13:15,956
-[SCOFFS]
-When he hurts you badly enough?

202
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:18,668
