203
00:13:18,752 --> 00:13:19,919
He will never hurt the children…

204
00:13:20,003 --> 00:13:22,673
You need to rent an apartment.

205
00:13:23,507 --> 00:13:27,510
Locally, if you don't wanna
disrupt the boys' school.

206
00:13:27,594 --> 00:13:30,847
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
We're getting way ahead of ourselves here.

207
00:13:30,931 --> 00:13:32,599
No, I don't think so.

208
00:13:32,683 --> 00:13:35,186
Stock the refrigerator,

209
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:38,898
make sure the utilities are paid
for, have the beds set up for the kids.

210
00:13:39,023 --> 00:13:41,109
