238
00:15:12,623 --> 00:15:15,292
Find a friend to confide in. Do it today.

239
00:15:16,293 --> 00:15:17,336
[SIGHS] Because…

240
00:15:17,461 --> 00:15:21,632
Because if there is a custody battle, you
know what Perry's lawyer will be asking.

241
00:15:21,716 --> 00:15:25,428
"Did you ever tell anybody, Mrs. Wright?"

242
00:15:25,512 --> 00:15:26,555
